A cold high-pressure system over North China hinders the southward migration of 
Mythimna separata in autumn.

Zhu J(1)(2), Chen X(3), Liu J(4), Jiang Y(4), Chen F(1), Lu J(1)(2)(5), Chen 
H(1)(2), Zhai B(1), Reynolds DR(6)(7), Chapman JW(1)(8), Hu G(9)(10).

Author information:
(1)Department of Entomology, Nanjing Agricultural University, 1 Weigang Road, 
