Extension for Community Healthcare Outcomes (ECHO) Chronic Pain & Opioid 
Stewardship in Northwestern Ontario: A Thematic Analysis of Patient Cases.

Poulin PA(1)(2)(3)(4), Shergill Y(3)(5), Grebowicz A(1)(6), Almeida I(3)(7), 
Cantave R(3), MacLeod B(1)(8), Larocque T(1), Garstin D(1), Fitzgerald SF(3), 
Rash JA(9).

Author information:
(1)St Joseph's Care Group, Project ECHO Chronic Pain & Opioid Stewardship, 
Thunder Bay, ON, Canada.
(2)Department of Psychology, Ottawa Hospital, Ottawa, ON, Canada.
(3)Clinical Epidemiology Program, Ottawa Hospital Research Institute, Ottawa, 
ON, Canada.
(4)Faculty of Medicine, Department of Anesthesiology and Pain Medicine, 
